<L>__{interior a hospital room. later}
<A>__{billy's mother lies as if floating in her bed. tubes, lights. a bald head on a barely dented pillow. she is a cancer patient in a coma, weighing possibly 80 lbs. gasping for air. her airways are cleared with a suction tube. billy sits watching as the tube goes in. billy sits looking at her.}
